
********************************************************************
			JQUERY ISSUU GALLERY PLUGIN
********************************************************************
Author: Marcos Timm Rossow
Web: http://marcos.blog.br/dev

=========================================
	DEMO: http://marcos.blog.br/issuu-gallery
=========================================


INSTALL:

Just add the JS Plugin file and CSS:

<script type="text/javascript" src="js/issuuGallery/jquery.issuu.gallery.min.js"></script>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="js/issuuGallery/css/style.css" />

USE:

JS:
$(function() {
	$('#gallery').IssuuGallery({user:'your_issuu_user_name'});
});

HTML:
<div id="gallery"></div>


Options accepted:

	user: '',
	size: 'small', // can be small, medium or large
	showDate: true, // display the publication date
	showTitle: true, // display the title of publication
	textOn: 'published in ', // text before publication date
	dateFormat: 'm/d/y', // can be: m/d/y or d/m/y
	colorBox: true, // If you want to use Colorbox (http://colorpowered.com/colorbox/) to show the publication. IF NOT, set False to link to issuu page
	loading: 'Loading publications...', // Loading Text
	proxyPath: '/issuuGallery/' // Path for the proxy file (proxy.php). This file is in the pack.
